data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: We are a marketplace dedicated to helping local artisans grow their businesses and bring their unique creations to a broader audience. Here, you’ll find a variety of handcrafted, high-quality products made with dedication and skill by artisans from all over the country. We believe that each piece deserves a place in the hearts of many and an opportunity to thrive.

data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value:
This app was developed by TPI, a team of students from Universitas Internasional Batam, with a vision to empower local artisan communities. Using C#, we’ve crafted a platform that offers you an easy, seamless shopping experience while helping artisans reach more customers.
With your support, we hope to keep growing and supporting even more local artisans. Thank you for being part of our community!
